ZH: 我需要仔细审视这份报告的内容。
EN: I need to carefully examine the content of this report.

ZH: 我们应当审视自己的行为，看看是否有什么需要改进的地方。
EN: We should examine our own actions and see if there is anything that needs improvement.

ZH: 他经常对自己的决定进行审视。
EN: He often reflects on his own decisions.

